The paper deals with the problem of teaching in multiagent reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus is on cooperative multiagent systems, which falls under the category of multiagent systems (cs.MA). The algorithm proposed in the paper involves coordination between agents, which is a key aspect of robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely for this paper.
